init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After hearing Bruce's pitch, the executives all agreed that his show sounded just like all of those other shows about families and relationships.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He went home that night and was a bit worried.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: His ex-girlfriend from over a decade ago.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: who gave Bruce the idea in the first place.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Carol was heartbroken, thinking she had wasted all of that time and effort.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was invited to the ABC Studios for a pitch meeting with Carol and the executives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When he arrived at the studios Carol was there, along with the other executives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Carol stared at him with her pale yellow eyes, and looked him over from head to toe.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Carol's eyes lit up and she smiled, revealing rows of perfect white teeth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was then that Bruce knew what was going on.
